  tags: ["paper", "surface", "reconstruction", "optimization"],
  lessons: [
    {
      zh: "若目标是可编辑网格，应在优化阶段显式偏向表面而非纯体渲染拟合。",
      en: "If the deliverable is an editable mesh, optimization should bias toward surfaces rather than volumetric overfitting.",
    },
    {
      zh: "泊松重建在规则化点云密度后仍是快速可扩展的网格提取工具。",
      en: "Poisson reconstruction remains a fast, scalable mesher once point distributions are regularized.",
    },
  ],
